---
description: Spec sync rule
globs:
  - "src/**/*.rs"
  - "Cargo.toml"
  - "openspec/specs/**"
alwaysApply: true
---

After any code change, review the relevant spec(s) under `openspec/specs/` and update them to reflect the current state. The specs are the living documentation ŌĆö code and specs must stay in sync. Each spec covers a distinct capability: `data-model`, `storage`, `mcp-server`, `cli`, `stdio-store`, `testing`.
